title: DanDanSoy
overview: Boyfriends Cardo and Nathaniel are happily living together in a rural part of the province. Even if their love helps to keep them going, they are starting to struggle to make ends meet. In need of money, Cardo hopes to find a job, but worries fill both their minds because of the COVID-19 pandemic. It could mean risking infection if they are to encounter outside people while on the job. In order to maintain a comfortable lifestyle, risks may need to be taken.
